  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink75-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattaiyōṭu puṉalāṭi vanta talaimakaṉ ataṉai maṟaittuk kūṟiyavaḻit tōḻi
          kūṟiyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink75">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>palariva ṇovvāy makiḻna vataṉā</l>
          <l>lalartoṭaṅ kiṉṟā lūrē malara</l>
          <l>toṉṉilai marutattup peruntuṟai</l>
          <l>niṉṉō ṭāṭiṉa ṭaṇpuṉa latuvē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> You are not like everyone else here, o delightful man. </l>
          <l> That's the reason that gossip has arised in the village.</l>
          <l> (They are saying) that she went bathing with you </l>
          <l> in the cool flood at the big ghat with its Myrobalan trees</l>
          <l> which have stood there for centuries, </l>
          <l> blooming. </l>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
